Bwiza Emerance ni umukobwa w'umunyarwandakazi akaba ari umwanditsi, umuririmbyi n'umuhimbyi, uri kuzamuka muri muzika nyarwanda  akaba arinawe wastinze irushanwa rya "The Next Diva _Indi Mbuto" ryabaye ku nshuro yaryo ya mbere. Aho arimo no twitegura kugaragaza alubumu yakoze yambere.

== UBUZIMA BWITE ==
Bwiza Emerance (yavutse 09 kanama 1999) ni umukobwa w'imfura iwabo mu muryango w'abana bane 4, mu bakobwa 2 n'abahungu babiri. akaba abana na Nyina na Se mu Mujyi wa Nyamata mu Akarere ka Bugeseramu intara y'uburasirazuba. Yavukiye i Gitarama, ni mukare re ka Muhanga mu intara y'amajyepho, umuryango uza kwimukira i kigali nyuma bajya gutura i Nyamata.<ref>https://www.eachamps.rw/Bwiza.html</ref>

=== AMASHURI YIZE ===
Bwiza Emerance amshuri abanza yayize kuri Kigali harvest ku kimihurura. Icyiciro rusange ( O Level, Tronc Commun), yize kuri Saint Joseph amaze gufata ishami ryo kwiga (A Level) yize kuri Saint Bernadette mu akarere ka Gisagara, asoreza ayisumbuye kuri Saint Aloys mu akarere ka Rwamagana mu intara y'uburasirazuba bw'u Rwanda. Bwiza Emerance yiga mu mwaka wa mbere muri Kminuza ya Mount Kenya mu ishami rya Hospitality and Tourism Management , aho yatangiye kwiga muri 2020.<ref>http://www.isimbi.rw/imyidagaduro/article/bwiza-emerance-yahigitse-abagera-kuri-210-yegukana-irushanwa-ryateguwe-na-kikac-music-label</ref>

=== IBIJYANYE NU MUZIKI ===
Uyu mukobwa ukiro muto Bwiza emerance Yakuze akunda umuziki ahanini biturutse ku kuba yarajyanaga n'ababyeyi be mu rusengero akishimira uko baririmba. Uko yigiraga hejuru mu myaka ni nako yajyag kuririmba muri korali zitandukanyezirimo iz'aban arabikomeza kugeza n'ubu. Uyu mukobwa yaririmbye muri korali kuva kumyaka 8 y'amavuko, ku buryo atazibuka neza amazina. Ndetse muri iki gihe ni umwe mu baririmbyi b'urusengero asengeramo rw'akoreraga i kigali nyuma rw'imukira i Nyamata. Akaba ashishikajwe cyane no gushyira itafari ku muziki w'abakorwa mu Rwanda, akagaragaza ko ibyo abahunga bakora n'abakobwa babikoramu muziki.<ref>https://umuryango.rw/imyidagaduro/article/bwiza-emerance-yahize-abandi-muri-the-next-diva-ahita-yakirwa-muri-kikac-music</ref>

=== IBIHEMBO ===
Bwiza Emerance akaba amaze kubona igihembo aho yatsinze irushanwa "The Next Diva-Indi Mbuto" ryabaye ku nshuro yaryo yambere,aho ry'ateguwe na KIKAC Music. Ibyo byamuhaye amahirwe y'oguhita atangira gufashwa n'iyi nzu isanzwe itunganya imiziki ikorana n'abahanzi mukubazamura baba menyekanisha bakaba barasinyanye amasezerano y'imyaka 5 bakorana, akaba amaze gukoreramo album ye yambere kugeza ubu ataraha izina ivuga k'urukundo n'ubuzima busanzwe, aho buri ndirimbo izajya isohokan n'amashusho yayo.<ref>https://inyarwanda.com/inkuru/108628/bwiza-emerance-yarangije-album-ya-mbere-yakozweho-nabarimo-madebeats-na-danny-vumbi-108628.html</ref>

